channel.title: Hi, I need help with teleports!
channel.description:
Hi, I need help with teleports!
I know how to change teleports from the emote tab, but I am unsure of how to change teleports on the mage tab. For example, I want Varrock to teleport to a training area instead of Varrock. I have right-clicked it and tried to find the number that showed up in my Client.Java, but I could not find it. I also tried looking at the command prompt after I teleported. I tried to find that number in my Client.Java, but I was out of luck also.
Can someone please help me, and tell me what to do? Thanks!
~Jc22493
P.S. - I'm not going to be a noob and say, "If you give me a good answer, I will rep you!", because I can't rep yet, and I won't lie about it.
Thanks again!
